img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b7f8455c3171210ed71b68bed2475bea9c8b3b","tid":710910,"uid":105166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T07:44:21.000Z","msg":"狗肉滾一滾，神仙企唔穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5da9d672c261a79fc14b205588535b10f35a57","tid":710910,"uid":82317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T07:58:23.000Z","msg":"我唔鍾意食田雞，唔通要全世界禁食？"},{"pid":"37e2e41210ab41e6d97696f04319a616b7a78882","tid":710910,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:01:31.000Z","msg":"納dee？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}